{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "Grocery App - Scene 4 (Validate in Grafana)",
    "tags": ["grocery-sre-demo", "custom", "scene-4"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 39,
    "version": 0,
    "refresh": "30s",
    "time": {
      "from": "now-1h",
      "to": "now"
    },
    "templating": {
      "list": [
        {
          "type": "custom",
          "name": "app",
          "label": "App",
          "query": "grocery-api",
          "current": { "text": "grocery-api", "value": "grocery-api", "selected": true },
          "hide": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    "panels": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "title": "Scene 4 — Validate with Grafana",
        "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "This dashboard supports the Grocery SRE storyboard Scene 4 (Validate with Grafana).\n\nIt expects a Loki datasource named **Loki (grocery)** and focuses on the inventory lookup scenario. If you haven't deployed Loki + the datasource yet, run: `demos/GrocerySreDemo/scripts/04-deploy-loki.sh` then `demos/GrocerySreDemo/scripts/07-create-custom-grafana-dashboard.sh`.\n\nWhat to watch after triggering the scenario:\n- Inventory failures spike (supplier throttling → 503s on inventory)\n- Failure % increases during the trigger window\n- Supplier rate-limit signals (errorCode `SUPPLIER_RATE_LIMIT_429`, retryAfter)\n\nIf you see **No data** in the inventory panels, generate inventory traffic by running: `demos/GrocerySreDemo/scripts/03-smoke-and-trigger.sh` or using the web UI’s **Check Inventory** / **Check All Inventory**."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Inventory requests (events/s)",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "sum(rate(({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=~\"inventory_check_(success|failed|error)|batch_inventory_check_started|batch_inventory_rate_limited|batch_inventory_partial_failure|batch_inventory_complete\")[$__interval]))"
          }
        ],
        "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
        "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Inventory failures (events/s)",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 5 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "sum(rate(({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=~\"inventory_check_(failed|error)|batch_inventory_rate_limited|batch_inventory_partial_failure\")[$__interval]))"
          }
        ],
        "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
        "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Inventory failure %",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 5 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "100 * (sum(rate(({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=~\"inventory_check_(failed|error)|batch_inventory_rate_limited|batch_inventory_partial_failure\")[$__interval])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=~\"inventory_check_(success|failed|error)|batch_inventory_check_started|batch_inventory_rate_limited|batch_inventory_partial_failure|batch_inventory_complete\")[$__interval])), 0.000001))"
          }
        ],
        "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100
          },
          "overrides": []
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Supplier rate-limit errors (events/s)",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 13 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "sum(rate(({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=\"supplier_rate_limit_exceeded\")[$__interval]))"
          }
        ],
        "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
        "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] }
      },
      {
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Rate-limit errors (last 15m)",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 13 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "sum(count_over_time({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=\"supplier_rate_limit_exceeded\" [15m]))"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
          "orientation": "horizontal",
          "textMode": "auto",
          "colorMode": "value",
          "graphMode": "none",
          "justifyMode": "auto"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "green", "value": null },
                { "color": "orange", "value": 1 },
                { "color": "red", "value": 10 }
              ]
            }
          },
          "overrides": []
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Supplier retryAfter (seconds) — p50/p95",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 13 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "quantile(0.5, avg_over_time(({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=\"supplier_rate_limit_exceeded\" | unwrap retryAfter [5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "p50"
          },
          {
            "refId": "B",
            "expr": "quantile(0.95, avg_over_time(({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=\"supplier_rate_limit_exceeded\" | unwrap retryAfter [5m])))",
            "legendFormat": "p95"
          }
        ],
        "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
        "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] }
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "title": "Top rate-limited products (count)",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 21 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "topk(10, sum by (productId) (count_over_time({app=\"$app\"} | json | event=\"supplier_rate_limit_exceeded\" [15m])))"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showHeader": true,
          "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Value", "desc": true }]
        },
        "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] }
      },
      {
        "type": "logs",
        "title": "Recent inventory failures (formatted)",
        "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 21 },
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "__LOKI_UID__" },
        "targets": [
          {
            "refId": "A",
            "expr": "{app=\"$app\"} | json | event=~\"inventory_check_failed|inventory_check_error\" | line_format \"{{.event}} product={{.productId}} code={{.errorCode}} retryAfter={{.retryAfter}} reason={{.reason}}\""
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": false,
          "showCommonLabels": false,
          "wrapLogMessage": true,
          "prettifyLogMessage": false,
          "enableLogDetails": true
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "overwrite": true,
  "message": "Create/update Grocery SRE Scene 4 dashboard"
}
